{"id":24,"date":"2017-09-13T16:05:07","date_gmt":"2017-09-13T07:05:07","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/xsig.hpcc.jp\/2018\/en\/?page_id=24"},"modified":"2017-09-13T16:05:07","modified_gmt":"2017-09-13T07:05:07","slug":"format","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/xsig.ipsj.or.jp\/2018\/en\/cf\/cfp\/format.html","title":{"rendered":"Paper Format"},"content":{"rendered":"<h3>Paper Format<\/h3>\n<dl>\n<dt>Language<\/dt>\n<dd>English or <a href=\"\/cfp\/format\/\">Japanese<\/a>.<\/dd>\n<dt>Necessary Items<\/dt>\n<dd>The format is not restricted as long as the following items are included\uff1a<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>\u201cxSIG 2017 Confidential Draft \u2014 Do NOT Distribute!\u201d at the top of the 1st page.<\/li>\n<li>Title<\/li>\n<li>Authors and Affiliations<br \/>\nxSIG is a single-blind workshop.<\/li>\n<li>Abstract<\/li>\n<li>Main Matter<\/li>\n<li>References<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Other items than these (e.g., acknowledgment) can be included (within word limits).<\/dd>\n<dt>Word Limits<\/dt>\n<dd>approximately 4,000 to 8,000 words.  No limit for references.  This would be 5 to 10 pages in 10pt, twocolumn styles.<\/dd>\n<dt>LaTeX<\/dt>\n<dd>If you use LaTeX, the following example will produce a paper that complies with the xSIG format.  Note that modifications are required depending on your style file.<\/p>\n<pre>\n\\documentclass[10pt, a4]{article}\n\n\\begin{document}\n\n\\twocolumn[\n  \\centering\n  xSIG 2018 Confidential Draft --- Do NOT Distribute!\\\\ \\vspace{5ex}\n  {\\LARGE Title}\\\\ \\vspace{4ex}\n  {\\large\n    Author1$^{\\dagger}$\\hspace{1em}\n    Author2$^{\\dagger}$\\hspace{1em}\n    Author3$^{\\ddag}$ % \u2026\n  }\\\\ \\vspace{2ex}\n  $\\dagger$: Affiliation1\\hspace{1em}\n  $\\ddag$: Afflication2\\\\ \\vspace{3ex}\n]\n\n\\begin{abstract}\nThis paper describes \u2026\uff0e\n\\end{abstract}\n\n\\section{Introduction}\n\nRecently, \u2026 \\cite{bib:xsig-2018}.\n\n\\begin{thebibliography}{99}\n\\bibitem{bib:xsig-2018} xSIG 2018, http:\/\/xsig.hpcc.jp\/2018\/en\/ (2017).\n\\end{thebibliography}\n\n\\end{document}\n<\/pre>\n<\/dd>\n<\/dl>\n<p>We will collect before the workshop the manuscripts for on-line distribution during the workshop.<\/p>\n<h3>Bachelor\/Master Thesis and Paper to Submit<\/h3>\n<p>We welcome papers that serves the base for bachelor\/master theses.<\/p>\n<p>However, a thesis and a papers to submit are different from the purpose. If you try to submit a paper that servers the base for your thesis, attention should be paid to the following items:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Do not write \u201cBachelor\/Master Thesis\u201d in the header.<\/li>\n<li>Include all the authors (including you).<\/li>\n<li>Do not write the adviser or the date of submission to the university office.<\/li>\n<li>Pay attention to the recipient and contents of the acknowledgement.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&lt;!&#8211;<br \/>\n\u524d\u8a18\u306e\u6587\u5b57\u6570\u30fb\u30ef\u30fc\u30c9\u6570\u5236\u9650\u3092\u8d85\u904e\u3057\u306a\u3044\u5834\u5408\u3067\u3042\u3063\u3066\u3082\uff0c\u6280\u8853\u7684\u5185\u5bb9\u306b\u6bd4\u3057\u3066\u9577\u3059\u304e\u308b\u8ad6\u6587\u306f\u4e00\u822c\u306b\u6e1b\u70b9\u306e\u5bfe\u8c61\u306b\u306a\u308a\u307e\u3059\uff0e\u7279\u306b\uff0c\u5352\u696d\u8ad6\u6587\u30fb\u4fee\u58eb\u8ad6\u6587\u306e\u30d9\u30fc\u30b9\u3068\u306a\u308b\u8ad6\u6587\u3092\u6295\u7a3f\u3059\u308b\u5834\u5408\u306b\u306f\uff0c\u4ee5\u4e0b\u3092\u63a8\u5968\u3057\u307e\u3059\uff0c\u3059\u306a\u308f\u3061\uff1a<br \/>\n\u80cc\u666f\u77e5\u8b58\u3092\uff0c<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>\u5f53\u8a72\u5206\u91ce\u306e\u5c02\u9580\u5bb6\u306a\u3089\u77e5\u3063\u3066\u3044\u308b\u3067\u3042\u308d\u3046\u4e00\u822c\u7684\u80cc\u666f\u77e5\u8b58 \u3068\uff0c\n<li>\u5f53\u8a72\u5206\u91ce\u306e\u5c02\u9580\u5bb6\u306b\u5bfe\u3057\u3066\u3067\u3082\u8aac\u660e\u3092\u8981\u3059\u308b\u3067\u3042\u308d\u3046\u8ad6\u6587\u56fa\u6709\u306e\u80cc\u666f\u77e5\u8b58<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em\">\u306b\uff0c\u7ae0\u30fb\u7bc0\u3092\u5206\u3051\u306